Welcome to ConfigurationManagement.Substitution
=====================

ConfigurationManagement.Substitution is a small sample project that shows 
how to manage configurations for several types of Visual Studio projects.

Substitution of configuration file happens on AfterBuild event. A user must 
add a custom MSBuild task that applies correct configuration depending on the
selected configuration in Visual Studio (or config passed to MSBuild or other build tool)

